## ğŸ“Œ **Overview**

This project uses **YOLOv5** to **detect, track, and alert** when a baby moves outside a **predefined safety zone**.

**Supports:**

* ğŸ¥ **Real-time webcam monitoring**
* ğŸ“‚ **Custom/local videos**
* ğŸ“º **YouTube videos**

**Goal** â†’ Build a **smart baby monitoring system** for nurseries, parents, or research purposes.

---

## ğŸš€ **Features**

* âœ… **Baby Detection** â€” Custom-trained YOLOv5 model.
* âœ… **Tracking** â€” Continuous frame-by-frame tracking.
* âœ… **Safety Zone** â€” Define a safe area to monitor.
* âœ… **Alert System** â€” Visual alerts when unsafe.
* âœ… **YouTube Integration** â€” Direct video processing from YouTube.
* âœ… **Google Colab-Friendly** â€” No need for a local GPU.

---

## ğŸ›  **Tech Stack**

| Tool/Library | Purpose                   |
| ------------ | ------------------------- |
| **Python 3** | Programming language      |
| **YOLOv5**   | Object detection          |
| **PyTorch**  | Deep learning             |
| **OpenCV**   | Video processing          |
| **yt-dlp**   | YouTube download          |
| **Pygame**   | Sound alerts (local mode) |

